Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙该不会忘记了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作真慢  你在磨蹭些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  我们迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  哪里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个美女是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹秋叶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是秋叶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来不知道你妹妹长得这么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是干有彦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次打电话来的那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  就是那个小干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候承蒙您照顾我哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  我才老是需要他照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这两位呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是同班的弓冢同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是Ciel学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟这位小姐不可能合得来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很没礼貌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法就是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟这一位绝对八字不合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是那么觉得吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还有办法忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学  学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真是让我感到意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到远野有个像秋叶小姐这样的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前没有提过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有听你提过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你们两个长得不太像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到哥哥会认识你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟学姐读同一所学校当然会认识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像Ciel小姐这样的人出现在哥哥身边就是不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好激烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶  你稍微节制一点好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还有办法忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样很没礼貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这是生理上的自然反应  我自己也没有办法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  没什么关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶的个性比较怕生  对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  就算一开始认为合不来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一段时间也有可能相处融洽的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这一位是绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶  你真的很顽固呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个状况如果那家伙在的话就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵  我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟我约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尝试下约会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天有约了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵  你来的真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  我刚刚没说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上她到我家来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来也没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是他妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我叫作Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟哥哥是什么样的关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能这么问…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着隐瞒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直借走志贵的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是承蒙您的照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  志贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我会好好听你解释的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在这里说话也没什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经严重警告过你了  你怎么好像完全听不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不听你的指挥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去坐什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的好像比较好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想和我作对？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要故意找碴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  两个都坐不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就这样决定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊叫飞车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋  你想破坏好不容易达成的共识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点太过刺激了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微锻炼一下身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多休息一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来要不要去玩那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来要不要去玩那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是两个人坐的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就要公平地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀  石头  布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气真差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小干一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我对不起你  行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  换个角度来想这说不定是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认为？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的确不是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连迟钝的你都能感觉到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟钝这两个字是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是直接说出事实而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你这个人就只会用这种方式说话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我很惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥对女性的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好跟我完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你是想摆脱罗嗦的妹妹好好喘一口气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没办法解释得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我这样做并不是讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  可以答应我─个任性的要求吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再跟那个人见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续这样下去真的没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是喜欢那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不说他可能一辈子也不会注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好棒的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太豪华了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在作梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都能吃到这么美味的东西  远野真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我家女佣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然哥哥好像不太喜欢的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明这么好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有说过不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前哥哥不是说过普通的食物比较好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真的很讨厌家里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野  是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以的话我随时都愿意跟你交换喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶  好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶你太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  志贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要去做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要勉强我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经很疲倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵  你没问题对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再缠着我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说缠着是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野不也是觉得很困扰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一点也不困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你自己这样想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,430)\fs-1}哎呀  这道筑前煮好像很好吃才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,430)\fs-1}这细腻的调味实在高雅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何只会这种自我中心的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请两位安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥身体状况并不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,430)\fs-1}这个三明治有着鸡肉和香草酱的香味挑起食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是他们在哥哥身边才会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最吵的是你  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说过哥哥已经累了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吵大闹的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是说你也有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野现在不就觉得很困扰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得大家一起来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来个完美的收尾大家去洗温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  大家好好来一次赤裸裸的交流…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种活动你也没办法参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真是败给他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他们的感情为什么那么差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是因为你的缘故了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这种事也不是现在才开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的迟钝算是一种自我保护吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我保护吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  让你想起了什么讨厌的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的或许对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次泡温泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid小姐你怎么看待远野的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢志贵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野只把我当成朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵对你的事情可是非常重视喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野对任何人都很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只对我特别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常羡慕Arcueid小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是恋人对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会成为那种对象的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对志贵来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是Arcueid小姐很漂亮身材又好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那种原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid小姐真是个很有趣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以稍微聊一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请长话短说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说远野八年前遇到意外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像没有当时的记忆了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为发生意外时的撞击让他失去记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这句话是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为这样解释比较方便吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野家好像有什么秘密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的很可疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么很可疑？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上有股跟人类不一样的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再跟你谈下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请转告我哥哥  我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  玩得真痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶她为什么先回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel学姐知道原因吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是拜托我转告而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事情吗？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↓Trailer↓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纠缠的红色长发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及用前后两面镜子照也没有见过的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:24:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  真月谭月姬“槛发”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.70,0:24:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家里藏着某种秘密  对不对？
